4, Balakov 2, Houbtchev 2, Sirakov, Stoitchkov, Kremenliev). Mexico: 14 (Alves 
3, Ramirez 3, Bernal 2, Suarez 2, Ramirez Perales 2, Garcia, Galindo). 
</P>
<P>
