</P>
<P>
 Yellow Cards -- Bulgaria, Kremenliev 13th minute, Sirakov 17th, Kiriakov 35th, 
Iordanov 68th. Mexico, Suarez 15th, Garcia 29th, Ramirez 71st, Garcia Aspe 
77th. 
</P>
<P>
