<P>
LOMELI'S HOME RUN LEADS CANOGA PARK, 6-4 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Gus Lomeli hit a tie-breaking three-run home run, leading Canoga Park to a 6-4 
victory over Sepulveda in a District 20 American Legion baseball game Tuesday 
at Faith Baptist High. 
</P>
<P>
 In other games, Las Virgenes defeated Woodland Hills East, 8-7, and Newbury 
Oaks beat Newbury Park, 10-3, in District 16 games. 
</P>
