<HEADLINE>
<P>
SIMPSON MURDER CASE; UNRESOLVED ISSUES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Municipal Court Judge Kathleen Kennedy-Powell has not yet revealed the 
contents of the bulky yellow envelope that Simpson's attorneys turned over last 
week. And court recessed Tuesday without a decision on the defense motion to 
suppress evidence seized during a search of Simpson's home after the 
killing.Discussion of the motion is expected to lead off today's hearing. MOVIE 
